# Architecture & Module Structure

## Top-Level Layout
```
src/
├── main.rs          # Minimal entry: mod declarations, ui::run()
├── models/          # Pure data structures, no UI/audio
└── threads/         # Engine, audio, UI
    ├── engine/      # Main loop, actions, synth
    ├── audio/       # cpal, buss, output
    └── ui/          # iced views, actions, components
```

## Models (Data Layer)
- **shared.rs**: Identifier types (`TrackIdentifier`, `RegionIdentifier`), `ProjectData`
- **components.rs**: Domain entities (Track, VirtualInstrument, etc.)
- **sequences.rs**: Sequence types, event streams, MIDI
- No dependencies on `threads` or `iced`

## Threads (Engine/Audio/UI)
- **Engine**: Receives `Actions` via mpsc, owns project data, sends `ProjectData` via flume
- **Audio**: `init_audio()` returns `(AudioEngine, StereoOutputController)`; uses `Output` trait
- **UI**: Iced application; subcomponents are structs with `view()` methods

## Identifier Pattern
- Newtype structs for IDs: `TrackIdentifier { track_id: usize }`
- Compose for nested IDs: `RegionIdentifier { track_id, region_id }`
